          <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">CHS</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">participants</ENAMEX> were somewhat healthier than the
          average older <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">adult</ENAMEX>; however, adjustment for detailed
