          These results are for <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">a 7-year</TIMEX> follow-up. The relative
          superiority of <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">YHL</ENAMEX> to <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">YOL</ENAMEX> would probably hold in trials
          with shorter follow-up. The effect sizes in <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">Table</ENAMEX> 3might
